{"type":"message","id":"e40b6afb","parentId":"6a43b12d","timestamp":"2026-02-18T19:05:51.445Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Wed 2026-02-18 21:05 GMT+2] OPERATION: CYBORG TRANSFORMATION (RUST LOGGER & IMMUNE SYSTEM).\n\n1.  **Rust Logger Integration (`scripts/log_compressor.py`):**\n    *   *Import:* `import src.rust_core as rust` (with try/except fallback).\n    *   *Logic:* Replace `hashlib.md5(line.encode()).hexdigest()` with `rust.validate_checksum(line)`.\n    *   *Benefit:* 40,000x faster deduplication.\n\n2.  **Immune System (`src/agent_wrapper.py`):**\n    *   *Import:* `from skills.system_doctor import doctor`.\n    *   *Pre-Flight:* `score = doctor.check()`.\n    *   *Guard:* `if score < 80: sys.exit(\"CRITICAL: System Unhealthy\")`.\n\n3.  **Proof of Speed (Benchmark Script):**\n    *   *Create:* `tests/perf/rust_1000_loop.py`.\n    *   *Loop:* 1000 iters of `validate_checksum`.\n    *   *Metric:* Avg time in microseconds (μs).\n\n4.  **Output:**\n    *   Logger update confirmation.\n    *   Immune System integration code snippet.\n    *   Benchmark Result (μs)."}],"timestamp":1771441551442}}
